2007-12-09  Christian Persch  <chpe@gnome.org>

	* glade/gnome/gnomecontrol.c: Don't define
	BONOBO_[UI_]DISABLE_DEPRECATED, or we'll get an undefined symbol "_".
	Fallout from bug #419535.

