	* configure.in: bump GTK+ and GNOME version requirements.

	* glade/gnome-db/gnomedblogindlg.c (gb_gnome_db_logindlg_new): 
	* glade/gnome-db/gnomedberrordlg.c (gb_gnome_db_errordlg_new): 
