2003-11-28  Damon Chaplin  <damon@gnome.org>

	* glade/gbwidgets/gbfilechooserwidget.c: 
	* glade/gbwidgets/gbfilechooserdialog.c: new files to support
	GtkFileChooserDialog and GtkFileChooserWidget.

